data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Plants of FSBI United Administration of the Lazovsky State Reserve and National Park Zov Tigra

Plants Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in FSBI United Administration of the Lazovsky State Reserve and National Park Zov Tigra (Russian Federation) consisting of 1627 records collected during 8 years between 2003 and 2016.
